859
00:40:58.873 --> 00:41:01.626
We heard the singing.
It was such beautiful singing.

860
00:41:02.710 --> 00:41:03.795
Tea?

861
00:41:03.878 --> 00:41:05.129
No tea.

862
00:41:05.672 --> 00:41:07.006
