996
00:47:58.042 --> 00:48:00.044
I think I found one of Alice's cookies.

997
00:48:02.338 --> 00:48:04.090
Hey. are you okay?

998
00:48:04.840 --> 00:48:07.176
My best friend just used me as live bait.

999
00:48:07.259 --> 00:48:09.303
You think I don't know how that feels?

1000
00:48:09.387 --> 00:48:11.472
My own father keeps coming after me.

1001
00:48:11.555 --> 00:48:12.932
I thought I knew Red.

1002
00:48:14.600 --> 00:48:15.851
I even defended her.

1003
00:48:16.394 --> 00:48:17.686
But I guess...

1004
00:48:18.854 --> 00:48:20.231
Never mind.

1005
00:48:20.314 --> 00:48:22.149
You want to see the good in everyone.

1006
00:48:22.817 --> 00:48:24.110
I never had that luxury.

1007
00:48:26.153 --> 00:48:28.697
I'm not interested in bonding
over being betrayed. Max.

1008
00:48:30.783 --> 00:48:32.284
Do you really think it could be hers?

1009
00:48:32.368 --> 00:48:33.786
I grew up hearing the stories.

1010
00:48:33.869 --> 00:48:34.870
Maybe they're true.

1011
00:48:34.954 --> 00:48:37.039
I mean.
what's the worst that could happen?

1012
00:48:37.123 --> 00:48:40.084
We get smaller and end up being eaten
by a bug or a squirrel.

1013
00:48:40.167 --> 00:48:41.836
or smushed under someone's shoe.

1014
00:48:44.505 --> 00:48:45.506
Who's hungry?

1015
00:48:47.007 --> 00:48:48.426
Thank you. Alice.

1016
00:48:48.509 --> 00:48:50.719
For the others. for when we find them.

1017
00:48:50.803 --> 00:48:53.722
Come on. guys. We've got a long way to go
to get to Maddox's cottage.

1018
00:48:53.806 --> 00:48:55.599
Let me guess. more walking.

1019
00:48:56.559 --> 00:48:58.185
Hang in there. Mom. Here we come.

1020
00:48:58.269 --> 00:48:59.895
Do you think the others are okay?

1021
00:48:59.979 --> 00:49:02.064
Don't worry.
They always land on their feet.

1022
