1032
00:49:42.146 --> 00:49:44.773
It's so cute!

1033
00:49:45.983 --> 00:49:47.193
Oh. wow.

1034
00:49:47.276 --> 00:49:49.153
White Rabbit likes his self-portraits.

1035
