01:02:50.433 --> 01:02:51.726
I hope not.

1298
01:02:52.227 --> 01:02:53.728
We rarely let go.

1299
01:02:54.354 --> 01:02:57.232
I wonder what the Oraculum will show you.

1300
01:02:57.315 --> 01:02:58.900
I'm not planning to use it.

1301
01:02:58.984 --> 01:03:01.236
This... ruined my father.

1302
01:03:01.319 --> 01:03:02.946
Ruined. empowered.

1303
01:03:03.029 --> 01:03:04.489
Potato. pot ah to.

1304
01:03:04.572 --> 01:03:06.324
I'm gonna use it to save someone instead.

1305
01:03:06.408 --> 01:03:10.537
What if I told you
your father was right all these years?

1306
01:03:11.121 --> 01:03:12.539
Ah. yes.

1307
01:03:13.081 --> 01:03:15.208
That's what you really
want to know. isn't it?

1308
01:03:15.750 --> 01:03:16.835
Good news.

1309
01:03:16.918 --> 01:03:20.296
The Oraculum can answer
all your questions.

1310
01:03:24.634 --> 01:03:25.844
What did my father see?

1311
01:03:27.262 --> 01:03:28.596
And why is it so important?

1312
01:03:31.891 --> 01:03:33.685
Showtime.

1313
01:03:39.566 --> 01:03:41.359
I am so proud of you. Max.

1314
01:03:43.653 --> 01:03:46.448
Get it right
or I'll show you punishment!

1315
01:03:46.531 --> 01:03:49.075
What your heart wants most.

1316
01:03:49.159 --> 01:03:50.326
My time machine.

1317
01:03:50.410 --> 01:03:52.537
When you alter the fabric of time.

1318
01:03:52.620 --> 01:03:54.956
there can be
some unpredictable consequences.

1319
01:03:55.040 --> 01:03:56.499
Off with her head.

1320
01:04:03.298 --> 01:04:05.008
Hearts!

1321
01:04:05.091 --> 01:04:06.092
In your time.

1322
01:04:06.176 --> 01:04:08.303
It's the perfect place
to keep this hidden.

1323
01:04:08.386 --> 01:04:09.429
A pocket watch.

1324
01:04:11.014 --> 01:04:12.474
I'm so proud...

1325
01:04:12.557 --> 01:04:14.350
There's no time.

1326
01:04:14.434 --> 01:04:15.769
I love you. son.

1327
01:04:20.690 --> 01:04:22.067
The pocket watch exists?

1328
01:04:22.150 --> 01:04:23.693
That life of my father.

1329
01:04:23.777 --> 01:04:25.779
-It was real?
-It was.

1330
01:04:25.862 --> 01:04:26.946
We looked happy.

1331
01:04:27.030 --> 01:04:28.323
And now you're not.

1332
01:04:28.406 --> 01:04:30.325
The redhead stole that life from you.

1333
01:04:36.623 --> 01:04:37.957
She lied to you.

1334
01:04:38.041 --> 01:04:40.043
She pretended to be your friend.

1335
01:04:40.710 --> 01:04:42.754
No way!

1336
01:04:48.635 --> 01:04:50.303
I never should've seen it.

1337
01:04:50.386 --> 01:04:52.138
But now that you have.

1338
01:04:52.222 --> 01:04:53.932
what are you going to do about it?

1339
01:04:56.351 --> 01:04:59.896
You can decide
your own fate and your father's.

1340
01:04:59.979 --> 01:05:02.774
if you can
get your hands on that pocket watch.

1341
01:05:14.619 --> 01:05:17.122
You know. Red's not the only one

1342
01:05:17.205 --> 01:05:19.374
who knows where the pocket watch is.

1343
01:05:19.457 --> 01:05:21.960
Anything she can't live without?

1344
01:05:28.383 --> 01:05:31.886
Revenge is a dish best served... blue.

1345
01:05:39.269 --> 01:05:42.063
♪ We were friends
We were close ♪

1346
01:05:42.939 --> 01:05:46.901
♪ How could I have
ever known that it would go ♪

1347
01:05:46.985 --> 01:05:49.821
♪ It would go this way ♪

1348
01:05:49.904 --> 01:05:51.281
♪ This way ♪

1349
01:05:51.990 --> 01:05:54.367
♪ Remember when we were cool? ♪

1350
01:05:55.160 --> 01:05:57.453
♪ I always had your back ♪

1351
01:05:58.037 --> 01:06:02.959
♪ Tell me how could you do me like that? ♪

1352
01:06:03.042 --> 01:06:06.045
♪ You're so heartless ♪

1353
01:06:06.129 --> 01:06:07.380
♪ Heartless ♪

1354
01:06:07.463 --> 01:06:09.841
♪ You hit me when my guard was down ♪

1355
01:06:10.425 --> 01:06:13.553
♪ And the hardest part is ♪

1356
01:06:13.636 --> 01:06:16.014
♪ That I let you let me down ♪

1357
01:06:16.097 --> 01:06:19.225
♪ How can you live with yourself? ♪

1358
01:06:19.309 --> 01:06:22.312
♪ You're not who I thought you were
You're someone else ♪

1359
01:06:22.395 --> 01:06:24.981
♪ There's no beating in your chest ♪

1360
01:06:25.732 --> 01:06:28.318
♪ Just the sound of emptiness ♪

1361
01:06:28.401 --> 01:06:29.986
♪ You're heartless ♪

1362
01:06:32.197 --> 01:06:33.531
♪ You played me from the start ♪

1363
01:06:33.615 --> 01:06:35.074
♪ But I've seen all of your cards ♪

1364
01:06:35.158 --> 01:06:37.952
♪ I can see your true intentions ♪

1365
01:06:38.036 --> 01:06:39.871
♪ Now I'm plotting my revenge ♪

1366
01:06:39.954 --> 01:06:41.456
♪ Your persona is pretend ♪

1367
01:06:41.539 --> 01:06:44.292
♪ And I think it's time
you learned your lesson ♪

1368
01:06:44.375 --> 01:06:46.169
♪ Behind that perfect princess ♪

1369
01:06:46.252 --> 01:06:47.879
♪ Is a nasty web of lies ♪

1370
01:06:47.962 --> 01:06:49.214
♪ Hearts are on your clothes ♪

1371
01:06:49.297 --> 01:06:51.174
♪ But you don't feel a thing inside ♪

1372
01:06:51.257 --> 01:06:52.258
♪ You know what you did ♪

1373
01:06:52.342 --> 01:06:56.930
♪ Can't believe you threw
my life away. away ♪

1374
01:06:57.013 --> 01:06:59.599
♪ I'll turn your nightmares to reality ♪

1375
01:06:59.682 --> 01:07:03.394
♪ My only strategy is your tragedy ♪

1376
01:07:03.478 --> 01:07:05.980
♪ You're not who you pretend to be ♪

1377
01:07:06.064 --> 01:07:08.149
♪ Yeah. you're just like me ♪

1378
01:07:08.983 --> 01:07:11.069
♪ 'Cause you're heartless ♪

1379
01:07:11.152 --> 01:07:12.487
♪ Heartless ♪

1380
01:07:12.570 --> 01:07:15.365
♪ And you'll never care how it feels ♪

1381
01:07:15.448 --> 01:07:18.368
♪ 'Cause you broke apart this ♪

1382
01:07:18.451 --> 01:07:21.329
♪ World I thought I had was real ♪

1383
01:07:22.038 --> 01:07:25.124
♪ I feel so betrayed
You switched up my fate ♪

1384
01:07:25.208 --> 01:07:27.335
♪ Now you're gonna get what you gave! ♪

1385
01:07:27.919 --> 01:07:29.754
♪ There's no beating in your chest ♪

1386
01:07:30.922 --> 01:07:33.299
♪ Just the sound of emptiness ♪

1387
01:07:33.383 --> 01:07:34.884
♪ You're heartless ♪

1388
01:07:36.844 --> 01:07:38.721
Max? What are you doing here?

1389
01:07:38.805 --> 01:07:40.348
♪ Yeah. I'm rough around the edges ♪

1390
01:07:40.431 --> 01:07:41.766
♪ But I'm not a bad guy ♪

1391
01:07:41.849 --> 01:07:45.144
♪ I can see the pain
that's been hiding in your eyes ♪

1392
01:07:45.228 --> 01:07:46.437
♪ I know how you're feeling ♪

1393
01:07:46.521 --> 01:07:48.189
♪ 'Cause our feelings intertwine ♪

1394
01:07:48.273 --> 01:07:49.691
♪ You seem like you need a friend ♪

1395
01:07:49.774 --> 01:07:51.276
♪ And right now so do I ♪

1396
01:07:51.359 --> 01:07:54.237
♪ You sound so sincere
but it's tough to open up ♪

1397
01:07:54.320 --> 01:07:55.822
♪ I'm angry and I'm hurting ♪

1398
01:07:55.905 --> 01:07:57.448
♪ And it's hard for me to trust ♪

1399
01:07:57.532 --> 01:08:00.243
♪ But here I am anyway
spilling out my guts ♪

1400
01:08:00.326 --> 01:08:01.869
♪ Well. I made you something special ♪

1401
01:08:01.953 --> 01:08:03.204
♪ And it's gonna cheer you up ♪

1402
01:08:03.288 --> 01:08:05.290
♪ Come on. try it on ♪

1403
01:08:05.373 --> 01:08:06.708
♪ You're gonna love it I swear ♪

1404
01:08:06.791 --> 01:08:08.209
♪ No. I couldn't
No. I shouldn't ♪

1405
01:08:08.293 --> 01:08:09.711
♪ No. I wouldn't even dare ♪

1406
01:08:09.794 --> 01:08:11.379
♪ See how it sparkles? ♪

1407
01:08:11.462 --> 01:08:13.047
♪ It's just like you ♪

1408
01:08:13.131 --> 01:08:14.299
♪ A part of me is scared ♪

1409
01:08:14.382 --> 01:08:16.009
♪ But I have nothing to lose ♪

1410
01:08:33.693 --> 01:08:34.986
♪ If you want heartless ♪

1411
01:08:35.069 --> 01:08:36.946
♪ I'll show you heartless ♪

1412
01:08:37.030 --> 01:08:39.490
♪ Crueler than you'll ever be ♪

1413
01:08:39.574 --> 01:08:43.244
♪ I'll be ruthless 'cause the truth is ♪

1414
01:08:43.328 --> 01:08:45.705
♪ You were never true to me ♪

1415
01:08:46.331 --> 01:08:49.375
♪ I feel so betrayed
You should be afraid ♪

1416
01:08:49.459 --> 01:08:52.170
♪ Now you're gonna get what you gave! ♪

1417
01:08:52.253 --> 01:08:54.922
♪ Now we're totally obsessed ♪

1418
01:08:55.006 --> 01:08:57.675
♪ 'Cause the wicked never rest ♪

1419
01:08:58.426 --> 01:09:00.553
♪ There's no beating in your chest ♪

1420
01:09:01.512 --> 01:09:04.015
♪ Just the sound of emptiness ♪

1421
01:09:04.098 --> 01:09:05.516
♪ You're heartless ♪

1422
01:09:07.643 --> 01:09:09.479
How'd you like
to dig up some buried treasure?

1423
01:09:24.327 --> 01:09:25.620
I'm not leaving without Chloe.

1424
01:09:26.329 --> 01:09:27.914
She didn't come back last night.

1425
01:09:27.997 --> 01:09:30.583
Neither did the prodigal son.

1426
01:09:30.666 --> 01:09:32.585
Max? Where did he go?

1427
01:09:34.087 --> 01:09:35.254
She's still not here?

1428
01:09:35.922 --> 01:09:38.007
I mean. she was pretty upset last night.

1429
01:09:38.800 --> 01:09:40.593
Yeah? What do you know about it?

1430
01:09:40.676 --> 01:09:42.678
I couldn't possibly
know anything. right?

1431
01:09:42.762 --> 01:09:43.763
'Cause I'm nice?

1432
01:09:44.472 --> 01:09:45.598
'Cause I'm happy?

1433
01:09:45.681 --> 01:09:49.435
You know. I choose
to find the joy in everything. Red.

1434
01:09:49.519 --> 01:09:51.145
But it doesn't make me naive...

1435
01:09:51.229 --> 01:09:52.688
...or dumb.

1436
01:09:54.691 --> 01:09:56.442
And it doesn't make me blind

1437
01:09:56.526 --> 01:09:58.695
to seeing people who tolerate me.

1438
01:09:58.778 --> 01:10:00.571
instead of actually care about me.

1439
01:10:03.741 --> 01:10:04.742
Chloe?

1440
01:10:05.576 --> 01:10:06.577
Chloe?

1441
01:10:07.203 --> 01:10:08.246
Where are they going?

1442
01:10:08.329 --> 01:10:09.414
Chloe?

1443
01:10:10.373 --> 01:10:11.749
Right. Me. too.

1444
01:10:13.376 --> 01:10:14.377
Look.

1445
01:10:14.877 --> 01:10:16.254
Leaving me behind again.

1446
01:10:17.046 --> 01:10:18.673
What am I. disposable?

1447
01:10:18.756 --> 01:10:21.592
Well. maybe you are. If you're just gonna
stand here and take it.

1448
01:10:26.264 --> 01:10:27.473
Wait for Pink. too!

1449
01:10:29.809 --> 01:10:31.936
I am good at giving advice.

1450
01:10:33.730 --> 01:10:35.231
Where are they running to now?

1451
01:10:35.314 --> 01:10:36.607
I don't know.

1452
01:10:39.527 --> 01:10:40.611
Hey. guys!

1453
01:10:40.695 --> 01:10:41.696
We were waiting for you.

1454
01:10:41.779 --> 01:10:43.239
Are we gonna get to the Oraculum?

1455
01:10:44.741 --> 01:10:46.868
And what's with the makeover?

1456
01:10:46.951 --> 01:10:47.952
Red.

1457
01:10:49.245 --> 01:10:51.497
You know. I wasn't having fun anymore

1458
01:10:51.581 --> 01:10:52.707
being good.

1459
01:10:52.790 --> 01:10:54.542
So I decided to do things your way.

1460
01:10:55.126 --> 01:10:57.503
Cruel... ruthless...

1461
01:10:59.672 --> 01:11:03.009
selfish... heartless.

1462
01:11:04.051 --> 01:11:05.178
Like the new me?

1463
01:11:07.346 --> 01:11:08.639
You can thank Max.

1464
01:11:09.891 --> 01:11:12.101
You did this? To my friend?

1465
01:11:12.185 --> 01:11:13.853
How quickly someone's life can change.

1466
01:11:14.979 --> 01:11:15.980
Right?

1467
01:11:16.689 --> 01:11:17.857
Hero to villain.

1468
01:11:17.940 --> 01:11:20.193
A simple flick of the switch or...

1469
01:11:21.444 --> 01:11:22.695
the wind of a watch.

1470
01:11:24.530 --> 01:11:25.531
Yeah.

1471
01:11:26.407 --> 01:11:27.408
That's right.

1472
01:11:28.284 --> 01:11:29.327
I know what you did.

1473
01:11:30.745 --> 01:11:32.872
How you ruined
my chances at a normal life.

1474
01:11:33.372 --> 01:11:34.874
A life that you now have.

1475
01:11:34.957 --> 01:11:36.959
Max. I never meant for that to happen.

1476
01:11:41.047 --> 01:11:42.215
It's time.

1477
01:11:42.298 --> 01:11:43.424
Ominous much?

1478
01:11:44.717 --> 01:11:47.220
Not Princess. just Red. right?

1479
01:11:47.303 --> 01:11:48.596
Maybe I can help with that.

1480
01:11:52.099 --> 01:11:54.185
I'm clearly
out of the loop. but this is bad. right?

1481
01:11:56.562 --> 01:11:57.897
I know what they're after.

1482
01:11:57.980 --> 01:11:58.981
Come on.

1483
01:12:03.486 --> 01:12:04.529
Wait!

1484
01:12:06.781 --> 01:12:08.366
Come on. Red!

1485
01:12:17.625 --> 01:12:18.626
Come on.

1486
01:12:19.585 --> 01:12:21.128
We need to get to the center and fast.

1487
01:12:21.712 --> 01:12:23.089
Oh!

1488
01:12:23.172 --> 01:12:25.675
Okay. How about. um... This way. Yeah.

1489
01:12:29.428 --> 01:12:30.468
I can hear them. This way.

1490
01:12:30.972 --> 01:12:32.390
Whoa! Look out!

1491
01:12:35.977 --> 01:12:37.228
This way.

1492
01:12:37.311 --> 01:12:38.354
Where are they?

1493
01:12:43.818 --> 01:12:45.069
-This way.
-No. wait.

1494
01:12:45.653 --> 01:12:47.113
-But we don't have time...
-Wait!

1495
01:12:48.030 --> 01:12:50.533
Three. two. one.

1496
01:12:59.417 --> 01:13:00.418
Come on.

1497
01:13:01.627 --> 01:13:02.795
Luis. there.

1498
01:13:03.838 --> 01:13:05.256
We'll never make it.

1499
01:13:05.339 --> 01:13:06.632
Yes. you will.

1500
01:13:06.716 --> 01:13:07.842
Go!

1501
01:13:07.925 --> 01:13:09.302
-What are you doing?
-Hurry!

1502
01:13:09.385 --> 01:13:11.387
I can't hold them off for long. Go!

1503
01:13:12.054 --> 01:13:14.015
Luis!

1504
01:13:14.557 --> 01:13:16.058
No!

1505
01:13:16.142 --> 01:13:18.519
I'll find you. I promise.

1506
01:13:19.145 --> 01:13:20.187
No. no. no. no.

1507
01:13:25.484 --> 01:13:26.485
Chloe?

1508
01:13:26.569 --> 01:13:27.820
Max. keep up.

1509
01:13:30.615 --> 01:13:32.158
Chloe?

1510
01:13:33.200 --> 01:13:34.201
Where are you?

1511
01:13:35.703 --> 01:13:36.954
Selfish.

1512
01:13:38.706 --> 01:13:39.916
Ruthless.

1513
01:13:42.084 --> 01:13:43.586
Ruined my life.

1514
01:13:45.671 --> 01:13:46.923
Hard to love.

1515
01:13:48.174 --> 01:13:50.092
You're such a disappointment.

1516
01:13:50.176 --> 01:13:51.677
Hearing things?

1517
01:13:52.386 --> 01:13:54.847
Warmer. Warmer.

1518
01:13:54.931 --> 01:13:57.475
Unlike them. I'm not in your head.

1519
01:13:57.558 --> 01:13:59.226
Chessy. leave me alone.

1520
01:13:59.310 --> 01:14:02.229
Not exactly crushing
this whole hero thing. huh?

1521
01:14:02.939 --> 01:14:04.815
I never asked for this.

1522
01:14:04.899 --> 01:14:06.484
Except you kinda did.

1523
01:14:07.485 --> 01:14:09.028
Now they all hate me.

1524
01:14:09.111 --> 01:14:11.364
Well. you did ruin the Hatters' lives.

1525
01:14:11.447 --> 01:14:12.740
got your mom captured.

1526
01:14:12.823 --> 01:14:15.326
left your boyfriend
in a shrub. and. oh. yeah.

1527
01:14:15.409 --> 01:14:18.037
nearly fed your bestie
to a bloodthirsty flower.

1528
01:14:18.996 --> 01:14:22.458
Didn't exactly
figure it out together. did you?

1529
01:14:23.542 --> 01:14:24.835
Leave me alone.

1530
01:14:33.260 --> 01:14:35.680
♪ I'm so lost and defeated ♪

1531
01:14:35.763 --> 01:14:39.976
♪ I've been climbing
but I keep getting knocked down ♪

1532
01:14:40.059 --> 01:14:42.937
♪ Down. down. down ♪

1533
01:14:44.563 --> 01:14:47.233
♪ How can a villain be a hero? ♪

1534
01:14:47.316 --> 01:14:51.529
♪ I don't even seem to recognize me now ♪

1535
01:14:51.612 --> 01:14:54.407
♪ Now ♪

1536
01:14:56.200 --> 01:14:59.537
♪ Every mistake's led me here ♪

1537
01:14:59.620 --> 01:15:04.166
♪ Now it's all up to me ♪

1538
01:15:07.628 --> 01:15:12.341
♪ Will I ever know who I am? ♪

1539
01:15:13.259 --> 01:15:18.222
♪ Will I ever get the chance? ♪

1540
01:15:19.390 --> 01:15:24.770
♪ Can I find the strength
that's deep inside me ♪

1541
01:15:24.854 --> 01:15:29.483
♪ Will ever understand ♪

1542
01:15:29.567 --> 01:15:31.402
♪ Who I am? ♪

1543
01:15:31.485 --> 01:15:34.196
♪ I made a mess and now my... ♪

1544
01:15:34.280 --> 01:15:36.449
♪ My time is running out ♪

1545
01:15:36.532 --> 01:15:40.369
♪ There's no second chances this time ♪

1546
01:15:40.995 --> 01:15:42.872
♪ No. whoa ♪

1547
01:15:42.955 --> 01:15:45.082
♪ This rebel deep inside ♪

1548
01:15:45.166 --> 01:15:47.960
♪ Won't go down without a fight ♪

1549
01:15:48.044 --> 01:15:53.340
♪ Won't give up till I make this right! ♪

1550
01:16:42.056 --> 01:16:43.057
Pink!

1551
01:16:44.183 --> 01:16:45.893
Pink. I need you.

1552
01:16:45.976 --> 01:16:47.311
-Pink!
-Red?

1553
01:16:49.146 --> 01:16:52.191
That's my sister in there.
and she needs me.

1554
01:16:52.775 --> 01:16:54.443
Open up this instant!

1555
01:16:56.320 --> 01:16:58.114
Oh. Thanks.

1556
01:17:02.243 --> 01:17:03.244
Red.

1557
01:17:07.665 --> 01:17:08.666
You came.

1558
01:17:08.749 --> 01:17:09.750
Of course.

1559
01:17:10.251 --> 01:17:11.752
That's what sisters do.

1560
01:17:14.338 --> 01:17:15.631
Where did you find that?

1561
01:17:16.549 --> 01:17:18.134
I remembered we left it here.

1562
01:17:22.429 --> 01:17:25.224
♪ Now I know who I am ♪

1563
01:17:25.307 --> 01:17:27.935
♪ Who I am ♪

1564
01:17:28.018 --> 01:17:32.189
♪ I finally have the chance ♪

1565
01:17:32.273 --> 01:17:33.983
♪ Have the chance ♪

1566
01:17:34.066 --> 01:17:39.613
♪ I can feel
the strength that's deep inside me ♪

1567
01:17:39.697 --> 01:17:44.160
♪ Now I understand ♪

1568
01:17:44.243 --> 01:17:46.787
♪ Who I am ♪

1569
01:17:48.956 --> 01:17:50.916
Pink. please tell me you still have

1570
01:17:51.000 --> 01:17:53.252
some of those cookies
left from the picnic.

1571
01:17:53.335 --> 01:17:54.336
Sure do.

1572
01:18:06.056 --> 01:18:08.767
Who's the big sister now?

1573
01:18:11.020 --> 01:18:12.021
Come on. Maddox.

1574
01:18:12.104 --> 01:18:13.647
-Just let us out.
-Please.

1575
01:18:13.731 --> 01:18:14.833
Think about your son.

1576
01:18:14.857 --> 01:18:16.567
Hmm.

1577
01:18:16.650 --> 01:18:19.278
Should've brought a bigger broom.

1578
01:18:19.361 --> 01:18:21.322
Time's up. Queens.

1579
01:18:21.405 --> 01:18:24.116
The pocket watch is nearly mine.

1580
01:18:25.409 --> 01:18:27.745
I'm so proud of you. Max!

1581
01:18:53.520 --> 01:18:54.521
Finally.

1582
01:18:55.606 --> 01:18:56.607
For my father.

1583
01:18:57.107 --> 01:18:58.484
For the life we could've had.

1584
01:18:59.026 --> 01:19:01.528
-For Red's betrayal.
-And my revenge.

1585
01:19:03.405 --> 01:19:04.406
Hey. guys.

1586
01:19:05.199 --> 01:19:06.200
Miss us?

1587
01:19:06.283 --> 01:19:07.701
Us?

1588
01:19:09.203 --> 01:19:10.663
Hi!

1589
01:19:23.509 --> 01:19:25.135
Red. are you okay?

1590
01:19:25.928 --> 01:19:26.929
Go. Pink.

1591
01:19:27.012 --> 01:19:28.180
Get the others.

1592
01:19:28.264 --> 01:19:30.766
Okay.

1593
01:19:30.849 --> 01:19:31.850
Where is it?

1594
01:19:32.601 --> 01:19:34.061
Where's the pocket watch?

1595
01:19:42.903 --> 01:19:44.280
Chloe...

1596
01:19:47.157 --> 01:19:48.701
Think about what you're doing.

1597
01:19:49.451 --> 01:19:50.494
This isn't you.

1598
01:19:51.078 --> 01:19:52.746
Weren't you listening. Red?

1599
01:19:53.747 --> 01:19:56.041
Of course it's not me.

1600
01:19:56.125 --> 01:19:57.668
Not the me that you knew. anyway.

1601
01:19:58.419 --> 01:19:59.712
No.

1602
01:19:59.795 --> 01:20:02.423
I'm free of her.

1603
01:20:02.506 --> 01:20:04.133
So click the dial. Chloe.

1604
01:20:04.216 --> 01:20:05.759
Our pain will disappear.

1605
01:20:05.843 --> 01:20:08.679
It'll all go away.
and she will be the one left hurting.

1606
01:20:08.762 --> 01:20:10.389
It's the perfect revenge.

1607
01:20:10.931 --> 01:20:13.017
Put our lives back the way they were.

1608
01:20:14.893 --> 01:20:15.894
Do it.

1609
01:20:17.521 --> 01:20:20.107
You think I'm doing this for you. Max?

1610
01:20:20.190 --> 01:20:21.650
Or your dad?

1611
01:20:23.319 --> 01:20:24.695
Aw.

1612
01:20:24.778 --> 01:20:26.739
No. I... I've seen the past.

1613
01:20:26.822 --> 01:20:29.533
I've seen that sad story.

1614
01:20:29.616 --> 01:20:32.661
No. I say we turn this around
and look to the future.

1615
01:20:34.413 --> 01:20:37.624
A future where I'll finally be on top.

1616
01:20:37.708 --> 01:20:38.917
and you'll know what it's like

1617
01:20:39.001 --> 01:20:40.961
to feel invisible and pushed aside.

1618
01:20:41.045 --> 01:20:43.547
A future where I won't need either of you.

1619
01:20:43.630 --> 01:20:45.632
-But I gave you that power.
-And I took it.

1620
01:20:45.716 --> 01:20:46.967
Chloe. you were right.

1621
01:20:47.051 --> 01:20:48.594
About everything.

1622
01:20:50.220 --> 01:20:51.388
Traveling to the past.

1623
01:20:51.930 --> 01:20:53.390
going back to save your mom.

1624
01:20:54.475 --> 01:20:55.684
changed my life.

1625
01:20:57.061 --> 01:20:59.563
I finally knew
what it was to do something good.

1626
01:20:59.646 --> 01:21:01.607
And that's because you believed in me.

1627
01:21:01.690 --> 01:21:04.651
You showed me that I wasn't a lost cause.

1628
01:21:05.361 --> 01:21:07.988
You had my back every single time.

1629
01:21:09.073 --> 01:21:11.658
I know these last few days
I haven't had yours.

1630
01:21:13.118 --> 01:21:14.119
But I do now.

1631
01:21:15.496 --> 01:21:16.622
I believe in you.

1632
01:21:17.831 --> 01:21:18.832
In us.

1633
01:21:21.418 --> 01:21:22.503
If you do this.

1634
01:21:23.295 --> 01:21:24.463
we lose everything.

1635
01:21:27.049 --> 01:21:28.550
We lose each other.

1636
01:21:30.260 --> 01:21:31.720
No. don't listen to her. Chloe.

1637
01:21:31.804 --> 01:21:33.514
Enough! Both of you!

1638
01:21:37.309 --> 01:21:38.644
♪ We'll figure it out ♪

1639
01:21:38.727 --> 01:21:40.687
♪ Figure it out together ♪

1640
01:21:42.648 --> 01:21:45.734
♪ Figure it out
Figure it out together ♪

1641
01:21:51.490 --> 01:21:52.533
♪ Figure it out ♪

1642
01:21:52.616 --> 01:21:55.119
♪ Figure it out together ♪

1643
01:22:07.965 --> 01:22:08.966
Chloe!

1644
01:22:12.136 --> 01:22:13.220
No!

1645
01:22:15.139 --> 01:22:16.974
This is your midnight. Maddox.

1646
01:22:17.057 --> 01:22:18.142
Time to go.

1647
01:22:19.643 --> 01:22:22.146
Ace for effort. though.
You really did give it your all.

1648
01:22:25.232 --> 01:22:26.233
Maddox...

1649
01:22:26.316 --> 01:22:27.996
We'll see who gets
the last laugh.

1650
01:22:32.906 --> 01:22:34.116
Oh. no.

1651
01:22:34.199 --> 01:22:35.284
No!

1652
01:22:36.368 --> 01:22:37.786
The watch!

1653
01:22:39.163 --> 01:22:40.581
It's mine.

1654
01:22:44.376 --> 01:22:45.586
Max. look out!

1655
01:22:49.631 --> 01:22:51.008
Please!

1656
01:22:54.511 --> 01:22:55.738
Together on three. Ready?

1657
01:22:55.762 --> 01:22:57.181
One. two. three!

1658
01:22:57.264 --> 01:22:58.700
It's gonna fall!

1659
01:22:58.724 --> 01:22:59.725
No. no. no!

1660
01:23:05.022 --> 01:23:06.398
-Are you okay?
-Yeah.

1661
01:23:19.119 --> 01:23:20.120
Thank you.

1662
01:23:22.206 --> 01:23:23.540
What about the watch?

1663
01:23:32.174 --> 01:23:33.342
What do we do with it now?

1664
01:23:36.261 --> 01:23:38.514
I'm sorry. Max. but we can't go back.

1665
01:23:39.848 --> 01:23:42.392
This has caused all of us enough pain.

1666
01:23:45.437 --> 01:23:47.439
Will you still try and help my father?

1667
01:23:47.523 --> 01:23:49.691
I won't abandon you or your dad.

1668
01:23:50.567 --> 01:23:51.652
I promise.

1669
01:24:12.923 --> 01:24:14.299
The pocket watch.

1670
01:24:14.383 --> 01:24:15.884
No!

1671
01:24:15.968 --> 01:24:17.427
I will destroy Wonderland!

1672
01:24:17.511 --> 01:24:19.763
-Come on. let's go!
-Thanks. Pink!

1673
01:24:19.846 --> 01:24:21.515
Knock knock.

1674
01:24:21.598 --> 01:24:22.599
Pink?

1675
01:24:22.683 --> 01:24:24.184
What in the hat?

1676
01:24:25.894 --> 01:24:27.187
Oh! Get him!

1677
01:24:27.271 --> 01:24:28.981
A-ha! There.

1678
01:24:30.440 --> 01:24:32.192
-Over here!
-Hook!

1679
01:24:34.528 --> 01:24:35.654
Now.

1680
01:24:40.784 --> 01:24:42.452
We did it!

1681
01:24:42.536 --> 01:24:43.954
Top that. Hatter!

1682
01:24:44.037 --> 01:24:45.515
You're not going anywhere. Hatter!

1683
01:24:47.332 --> 01:24:48.917
Oh. someone's stuck.

1684
01:24:49.001 --> 01:24:50.502
Not bad for a pirate.

1685
01:24:51.044 --> 01:24:53.547
Look at you.
Hair still perfectly in place.

1686
01:24:53.630 --> 01:24:54.881
Heh. It's a talent.

1687
01:25:07.144 --> 01:25:09.438
I missed you. I missed you. and you...

1688
01:25:09.521 --> 01:25:10.522
Mom.

1689
01:25:11.481 --> 01:25:12.482
-My darling.
-Mom?

1690
01:25:12.566 --> 01:25:14.651
Ah. Red.

1691
01:25:15.986 --> 01:25:17.029
Dad.

1692
01:25:17.112 --> 01:25:18.548
Oh. I'm so happy to see you.

1693
01:25:18.572 --> 01:25:19.573
Hmm.

1694
01:25:20.365 --> 01:25:22.659
-You're okay.
-Yes. Are you?

1695
01:25:22.743 --> 01:25:23.744
Uh. yeah.

1696
01:25:23.827 --> 01:25:25.537
-I missed you.
-Oh. honey.

1697
01:25:26.747 --> 01:25:28.999
-I like the pants.
-Me too.

1698
01:25:32.753 --> 01:25:35.088
-I can't believe you made it.
-Hey. guys.

1699
01:25:35.172 --> 01:25:36.965
Pink saved us with cookies.

1700
01:25:37.049 --> 01:25:38.425
-You all right?
-Yeah.

1701
01:25:38.508 --> 01:25:41.136
How dare you come into my palace.

1702
01:25:42.262 --> 01:25:44.431
endanger my children.

1703
01:25:44.931 --> 01:25:47.768
and use my magic against me?

1704
01:25:47.851 --> 01:25:51.146
Off with his head!

1705
01:25:55.567 --> 01:25:58.737
Where in heavens
did that come from?

1706
01:25:58.820 --> 01:26:01.490
Guards. Take him away.

1707
01:26:01.573 --> 01:26:03.575
-No. Dad.
-Stop. You can't.

1708
01:26:04.076 --> 01:26:05.285
This is all my fault.

1709
01:26:07.162 --> 01:26:08.163
It's true. Mom.

1710
01:26:10.040 --> 01:26:12.125
Maddox. I'm sorry about everything.

1711
01:26:15.587 --> 01:26:17.255
This all started because I was too afraid

1712
01:26:17.339 --> 01:26:18.757
to stand up for what was right.

1713
01:26:19.716 --> 01:26:21.134
Too afraid to disappoint you.

1714
01:26:22.177 --> 01:26:23.804
Then. and now.

1715
01:26:25.138 --> 01:26:26.640
I'm no hero. Mom.

1716
01:26:27.891 --> 01:26:30.686
It's what a person does that defines them.

1717
01:26:31.603 --> 01:26:33.188
Hero?

1718
01:26:33.730 --> 01:26:35.065
That's just a word.

1719
01:26:36.733 --> 01:26:37.734
Then...

1720
01:26:39.194 --> 01:26:40.445
maybe so is villain.

1721
01:26:41.947 --> 01:26:43.699
Maybe everyone deserves a do-over.

1722
01:26:48.870 --> 01:26:50.622
He can keep his head.

1723
01:26:51.790 --> 01:26:53.208
Hm.

1724
01:26:53.291 --> 01:26:57.671
But he can also
stay cozy in there for a little bit.

1725
01:27:02.634 --> 01:27:04.302
So I heard you have a dark side.

1726
01:27:04.928 --> 01:27:06.555
Nice.

1727
01:27:06.638 --> 01:27:08.223
Maybe I was wrong about you.

1728
01:27:09.182 --> 01:27:11.935
Yeah. Me too.

1729
01:27:13.687 --> 01:27:15.564
This calls for a celebration.

1730
01:27:16.356 --> 01:27:18.525
Let's throw a party.

1731
01:27:18.608 --> 01:27:21.403
A tea party.

1732
01:27:21.486 --> 01:27:22.547
Let's throw a tea party.

1733
01:27:22.571 --> 01:27:23.572
No.

1734
01:27:26.742 --> 01:27:28.660
I love throwing parties.

1735
01:27:32.622 --> 01:27:34.750
-To replace the old one.
-It's so good.

1736
01:27:39.504 --> 01:27:41.506
Mom. I owe you an apology.

1737
01:27:41.590 --> 01:27:42.674
And I. you.

1738
01:27:42.758 --> 01:27:45.177
