parts of you away if you're not careful.

1742
01:27:52.768 --> 01:27:54.811
But you helped me find them again.

1743
01:27:54.895 --> 01:27:56.354
and I'm so grateful.

1744
01:27:59.065 --> 01:28:00.400
Mm.

1745
01:28:00.484 --> 01:28:02.611
Now. what's the deal with evil Chloe?

1746
01:28:03.487 --> 01:28:05.280
I... I don't know
what you're talking about.

1747
01:28:05.363 --> 01:28:07.091
I promise
I won't tell your father.

1748
01:28:16.166 --> 01:28:17.250
You made it out.

1749
01:28:17.334 --> 01:28:19.211
Those hedges got nothing on me.

1750
01:28:21.129 --> 01:28:22.172
I owe you one.

1751
01:28:23.799 --> 01:28:25.133
By my calculations.

1752
01:28:25.717 --> 01:28:26.718
