1753
01:28:27.219 --> 01:28:29.346
I can't with you.

1754
01:28:36.561 --> 01:28:37.646
A toast.

1755
01:28:39.731 --> 01:28:43.652
I'd like to toast
to the bravest rescuers I've ever known.

1756
01:28:43.735 --> 01:28:46.905
What you all endured these past days.

1757
01:28:46.988 --> 01:28:49.741
the way you all worked together

1758
01:28:49.825 --> 01:28:52.410
and overcame tremendous odds.

1759
01:28:52.494 --> 01:28:55.163
it's... inspiring.

1760
01:28:55.247 --> 01:29:00.001
And we are forever proud
of each and every one of you.

1761
01:29:08.343 --> 01:29:10.971
P.S.. I think your mom likes me.

1762
01:29:11.930 --> 01:29:13.348
Oh. my...

1763
